(64,'wc_com_in_person_payments_card_sale_UK_inbox_note_q4_23','marketing','en_US','Save 35% on a WooPayments card reader','Have you been thinking about selling your products or services in person? Nows the perfect time to do so, as were discounting our WisePad 3 card readers by 35%! Securely process payments wherever your business takes you, with full store and inventory sync. Dont miss out  this offer ends 29th October 2023.','{}','pending','woocommerce.com','2023-10-25 14:54:33',NULL,0,'plain','',0,0,'info'),
